title: Jackdaws
description:
This spacious apartment with a balcony or terrace is available for rent in sector 24, gandhinagar.

This apartment is well ventilated and has ample parking facility.
With a balcony or terrace, this apartment has a good community view.
Facing is towards the green and peaceful nature of the area.
Ample green spaces, parks and open spaces are present in the vicinity of the apartment.
Being located in a safe and secure locality, the neighbourhood is also well developed.
At a rent of Rs 21000, this apartment is Semi-Furnished and comprises of a good 1100 square feet of space.
Comprising of 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms, this apartment is suitable for a family.

title: Robins Hedge
description:
